nodes.text:
An unidentified 2-1B surgical droid was working as a bartender at Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina on the planet of Tatooine during the Clone Wars.
Around 21 BBY, this droid was serving drinks at the bar when several bounty hunters, including former Dark Acolyte Asajj Ventress, were looking at a holopanel for the latest bounties.
